Name: Radiant Synthseed
Description: These crystals vibrate at soothing harmonic frequencies when exposed to natural sunlight. When crushed, the powder make a delightfully invigorating snuff. Rare, though generally found in hills and mountains near coastal regions. VALUE20-30VALUE GP
Types: Bomb, Gas, Potion
Bomb: Double the number of all damage dice for this bomb.
Gas: Creatures within this gas have advantage on saving throws against being Charmed or Frightened, and cannot be put to sleep magically.
Potion: A creature ingesting this potion gains advantage on Charisma checks and saving throws for one minute.
